data.description: Your dream country retreat in the southern part of Senoia awaits. This serene haven offers the perfect blend of country tranquility with modern comfort and conveniences of Peachtree City only 15 minutes away. As you drive on Highway 85, the rolling landscape is beautiful and the pecan trees welcome you home as you pull into the driveway. Step into security and comfort as you enter this beautiful brick 3-bedroom, 2-bath home. Kitchen has been upgraded with custom cabinets and new appliances in 2019  along with sparkling quartz countertops and backsplash. It is truly a chef's delight. Step out on the newly painted deck and enjoy entertaining friends with countryside views. The sale includes 2 adjoining lots totaling 3.8 acres of level property with a  pond at the back. The fenced front yard is perfect for your pets to step outside and be secure.   Meticulously maintained and updated, this property received a brand new roof in November of 2023 which has a transferable warranty! In 2019, a new septic tank and new field lines were installed. All doors, windows, floors, and appliances were upgraded in 2019. The basement has been moisture protected by Aquaguard and there are maintenance free rain gutters. The home is accessible with ramps and most doors are 30 inches wide.   The owner wants to make a fresh start in 2024 and has expressed an interest in making his move easier by negotiating any furniture or electronics that you are interested in. Don't miss your chance to make a great start in 2024 by moving into this wonderful south Senoia home!
